Recommended Buckets Alert

Indicates that, for a numerical value, Einstein Discovery devised an alternative set of buckets. Bucketing is key to making your insights interpretable. Try using the recommended buckets in your model.

Einstein Discovery uses Kernel Clustering Density, an unsupervised machine learning algorithm, to analyze numerical data. The alert indicates that the clustering algorithm determined an alternate set of bucket ranges.
